				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ T(\lambda ) = \frac{{(1 - R)^{2} }}{{(1 - R)^{2} + 4R\sin^{2} (4\pi \,nd/\lambda )}}, $$\end{document}where R is the reflection coefficient of the film surface.

